A small mammal with a long tail and pointed ears.
The $(this.trait:build) body is sinuous and flexible.
There is a claw at each end of the cat's toes.
A pair of delicate, but sharp pointed ears.
A pair of delicate, but sharp pointed ears.
The eyes of the cat are located on either side of its head. They are perfectly round and contain a large black pupil surrounded by a rim of gold. The cat looks back at you almost intelligently.
Large circular unblinking eyes with black pupils and golden irises.
The forelegs are long and agile.
The fur looks smooth, and is of a $(this.trait:color) color.
A triangular head, with large circular eyes.
A small nose with whiskers. The cat occasionally moistens its nose with a long, pink tongue.
A collection of four paws with sharp, hooked claws.
A collection of four paws with sharp, hooked claws.
The rear legs are long and agile.
The tail is nearly as long as the rest of the body.
